# Defense-in-depth headers on every page served by Pages. CSP is set here
# (and not on the Worker) because this app actually ships HTML; the Worker
# mostly serves JSON where CSP has no DOM to govern.
#
# CSP notes:
# - script-src 'self' — strict; no inline scripts.
# - style-src includes 'unsafe-inline' because SvelteKit emits hydration
#   styles that way; tightening would require nonces wired into the SSR.
# - font-src allows fonts.gstatic.com (the Plex / Playfair files); the
#   stylesheet itself comes from fonts.googleapis.com under style-src.
# - frame-ancestors / base-uri / object-src locked down.
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), camera=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'; form-action 'self'
